3400:Sena was still frozen in place, looking at me with tears in her eyes as she cradled the baby.\p;
3500:Over half of the white towel was now covered in a deep shade of red.\n;I could no longer tell if that blood was mine, or the baby's.\p;
3600:〔Sena〕“Nishijou... You're... You're bleeding...!”\p;
3700:〔Sena〕“If you don't stop, you'll...!”\p;
3800:〔Takumi〕“W-We'll use the ch-cheat code...”\p;
3900:〔Sena〕“B-But... what... do I do...?”\p;
4000:Th-This wasn't good... I was gonna lose consciousness...\p;
4100:It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts! It hurts!\p;
4200:I never asked to go through pain like this...\n;With the cheat code, I should be invincible, but if Sena doesn't activate it, I'm gonna die...\p;
