4800:〔Sena〕“Wah... Aa... aah...!”\p;
4900:Sena only continued to cry.\n;...This was it. After all that grinding to get the cheat code, none of it mattered in the end...\p;
5000:〔Man〕“...Burn in hell, you little shit.”\p;
5100:The sensation on my back suddenly disappeared.\n;I thought I'd just been shot, but it wasn't a gunshot that I'd heard—it was the sound of the air itself shaking.\p;
5200:〔Man〕“Aah...! Aaahhh...! M-My... my arm...!”\p;
5300:White feathers...\n;...shimmered and danced through the air.\n;But we were underground. There shouldn't have been any birds here.\p;
5400:Despite my consciousness turning foggy, and the pain ripping through my entire body, I slowly managed to turn around.\p;
5500:And there I saw...\p;
5600:〔Takumi〕“Ri...mi...?”\p;
5700:〔Rimi〕“Taku...”\p;
5800:Clasped in her hands was a sword so elegant, so beautiful... yet its form was unendingly sinister...\n;I'd never seen anything like it.\p;
5900:It was Rimi.\p;
6000:Rimi, who had disappeared on me before, was here.\n;She looked at me with a smile filled with sorrow.\p;
6100:A large quantity of blood poured from the man's arm. Everything from the elbow down had been severed.\n;The hand holding the gun rolled around on the ground.\p;
6200:Had... Rimi done that...?\p;
6300:〔Man〕“Y...ou... bitch...! M-My... hand...! How dare you...!”\p;
6400:〔Rimi〕“With all the horrible things you did to Nana-chan, this is nothing.”\p;
6500:〔Takumi〕“Ri...mi...”\p;
6600:Rimi avoided my dumbfounded gaze.\n;She simply stood in front of the man, shielding us.\p;
6700:〔Rimi〕“Get out of here, now. I've got the gist of what's going on.”\p;
6800:〔Rimi〕“Aoi-san! Taku! Destroy Noah II!”\p;
6900:That sharp voice brought me back to my senses.\n;But when I tried to move my body, even just a little bit, I was tortured by unrelenting pain.\p;
7000:I wanted to collapse on the spot.\n;I didn't want to move... I didn't want to think... but most of all, I didn't want to die.\p;
7100:My consciousness was fading.\n;I was fully aware of the blood flowing out of the wounds covering my entire body.\p;
7200:Despair and the fear of death threatened to overwhelm me, but I fought them back and held onto Sena's shoulders.\p;
7300:〔Takumi〕“Let's go...”\p;
7400:〔Takumi〕“While... we s-still can...”\p;
7500:〔Sena〕“*sniffle*... I'm sorry, Nishijou...”\p;
7600:〔Sena〕“You... shielded me... *sniffle*... and now you're... *sob*...!”\p;
7700:Sena's eyes were clouded with tears.\n;It was the first time I'd ever seen her crying face.\n;I guess even level-headed women like Sena cried sometimes...\p;
7800:I noticed something else as I held her shoulders.\p;
7900:Her body was incredibly frail.\n;I was sure that wasn't unique to Sena—it probably applied to all IRL girls, really.\n;Her body was slender as well, something guys also didn't share.\p;
8000:On a normal day, she exuded an aura of confidence, arrogance, and so much overwhelming vigor, it felt like she could crush me with it... but at the end of the day, she really was still a girl.\p;
8100:It'll be all right. Don't cry, Sena. If we just use the cheat code, it'll heal all these wounds in an instant... It has to...\p;
8200:Believing that, I grit my teeth and walked forward.\p;
8300:Behind me, I heard the sound of a strange mechanical sound and a shrieking resonance entangling with one another, but I refused to look back anymore.\p;
